":"好撚無聊呀左膠"},{"pid":"7a6ea3910f95f87cdab4e5bc660b0065cb0b7c10","tid":1082140,"uid":27530,"like":39,"dislike":4,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T18:17:32.000Z","msg":"影片無探討過現實社會係咪男人做得好啲導致同工不同酬"},{"pid":"b67e161a5fff6c6af2ee6402c855afe0b01ad9a4","tid":1082140,"uid":17232,"like":123,"dislike":3,"score":120,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T18:19:53.000Z","msg":"最撚憎女權撚將所有事簡單化<br />\n同工不同酬明明係一個好複雜嘅議題 裡面有好多唔同嘅因素導致 但係佢地就淨係將同工不同酬歸咎於性別嘅分別上面 <br />\n<br />\n仲要淨係同個細路講你攞得少獎 因為你係女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26becff980fe07d463905ae7a7862e98c410bf0f","tid":1082140,"uid":2974,"like":94,"dislike":3,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"香港版本：女孩發現自己得到的獎賞比男孩少時，決定公開數年前被男孩性侵的經過"},{"pid":"6bb5e7abf765706bc647a9e754b1262ba293e2b0","tid":1082140,"uid":49575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T18:28:16.000Z","msg":"前排請廚師助理張圖呢？"},{"pid":"0f7db346ace4c0df651f216fdcf9306be0535072","tid":1082140,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T18:39:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c717e30d3fcc44ced5b8c7156a5090e4c76e8e7d","tid":1082140,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bb5e7abf765706bc647a9e754b1262ba293e2b0","tid":1082140,"uid":49575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T18:28:16.000Z","msg":"前排請廚師助理張圖呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T18:40:02.000Z","msg":"咩圖"},{"pid":"4379601b9b531e7586044dc14b8a7a0f0c83952b","tid":1082140,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T20:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6be4c22f22534c3790f627d0bde41b6e6967996","tid":1082140,"uid":97240,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T21:02:02.000Z","msg":"金髮唔係女咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黑人細路唔係係男咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f9807ab927ac2327c1714766a43ea60ae1fe15","tid":1082140,"uid":45120,"like":26,"dislike":5,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T21:19:21.000Z","msg":"明明就係平均女人工作能力係比男人低<br />\n又唔承認就怪去人地因為你性別問題<br />\n女人永遠簡單野就諗到好複雜<br />\n複雜野又諗到好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2434e76a2eb55a4a3dbb0b77271e2ecd05a17bda","tid":1082140,"uid":59641,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T22:12:24.000Z","msg":"資本主義下根本冇可能單純因為性別而同工唔同酬<br />\n<br />\n如果女真係平啲又做到一樣嘅事冇人會特登貴啲請個男嘅返嚟做"},{"pid":"5fbfc390f17228c51f1ad86bc971eedb0fef7bea","tid":1082140,"uid":14459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:19:32.000Z","msg":"屌唔怪得咁多正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589ce273989f161b391c7acd2f30f73eb3f06ad1","tid":1082140,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T00:35:49.000Z","msg":"死唔斷氣既話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60299f22585d4cc18e4c425f2c67d67a3782632c","tid":1082140,"uid":135957,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T01:59:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"536c0d4bbab2489ca1eaecf45a48494384ac26ae","tid":1082140,"uid":49575,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"c717e30d3fcc44ced5b8c7156a5090e4c76e8e7d","tid":1082140,"uid":17232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6bb5e7abf765706bc647a9e754b1262ba293e2b0","tid":1082140,"uid":49575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T18:28:16.000Z","msg":"前排請廚師助理張圖呢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T18:40:02.000Z","msg":"咩圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"[有圖] 搵食艱難，而家做個廚房助理都要有閪先做得！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1075596\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1075596</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/9Hwf9Zc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hwf9Zc.jpg&h=d6e917f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"498b5233711412ab6c293a0ae6fc67ade6bcb6de","tid":1082140,"uid":55511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:30:30.000Z","msg":"左膠原本已經on9 仲要教埋下一代呢啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d76dbf265f4eaefb5e15ec4f7d7dd750fa1f1eb","tid":1082140,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:31:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5ab640e345f8432be560e1b155fa6adaf298cd5","tid":1082140,"uid":112436,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"喺現代化/自由社會之下，男女嘅同工不同酬根本就唔存在。<br />\n如果男女真係能夠做到exactly一樣嘅嘢，而人工又真係男高過女，咁所有公司都會因為成本因素而只會請女性而唔會請男性。"},{"pid":"71b8be7a741a9e4130fb5fd3e3228cccd4685237","tid":1082140,"uid":27935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:00:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99cc4b26ffede05e8bbb6a1b279b535f75d9990c","tid":1082140,"uid":95520,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:03:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/52XsQhH-wls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F52XsQhH-wls&d=88BycQanWGa6BXzVat85HTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=4984defc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/52XsQhH-wls</a><br />\n其實bill burr講得幾好<br />\n<br />\n點解我哋每個鐘可以多你哋一蚊usd嘅人工啊?<br />\n因為遇到鐵達尼事件嘅話<br />\n我哋要讓你哋上船<br />\n然後我哋成個傻仔咁跌落海死"},{"pid":"4f5ac1ce2718ce3f041bcda6c3fc7216f57ad71b","tid":1082140,"uid":88029,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:12:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ead7b70dce961fb059ca6946b9a6d67920a4df15","tid":1082140,"uid":18167,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T03:19:58.000Z","msg":"福利要好過男人(有薪月經假), 工作要少過男人(粗重要男人做), 人工要一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}